          "_name": "features021",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features21\" plugins=\"Masonry\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Center Image\" name=\"centerAlign\" condition=\"showImage\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n      <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n      <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n    </select>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-0 content-head\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n          <b>Why another Framework?</b></h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n          List main features of your project in this block\n        </h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row mbr-masonry\" data-masonry=\"{&quot;percentPosition&quot;: true }\">\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n              <img src=\"../_images/shop/shop1.jpg\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n              <b>Modularity</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent\n              vitae erat. Integer aliquam, lorem vitae dapibus sollicitudin,\n              nibh nisl egestas enim, ut dapibus odio augue venenatis mi. Ut\n              tempus dui at mi semper, vel dapibus nisl consectetur. Phasellus\n              consectetur sapien non lacus imperdiet dapibus. In facilisis sed\n              mi rutrum consequat. Sed augue sem diam.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n              <img src=\"../_images/shop/shop2.jpg\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n              <b>Reusable logic</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent\n              vitae erat. Integer aliquam, lorem vitae dapibus sollicitudin,\n              nibh nisl egestas enim, ut dapibus odio augue venenatis mi.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n              <img src=\"../_images/shop/shop3.jpg\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n              <b>Custom Needs</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent\n              vitae erat. Integer aliquam, lorem vitae dapibus sollicitudin,\n              nibh nisl egestas enim, ut dapibus odio augue venenatis mi. Ut\n              tempus dui at mi semper, vel dapibus nisl consectetur. Phasellus\n              consectetur sapien non lacus imperdiet dapibus. In facilisis sed\n              mi rutrum consequat. Sed augue sem diam.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n              <img src=\"../_images/shop/shop3.jpg\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n              <b>Design</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              Ut tempus dui at mi semper, vel dapibus nisl consectetur.\n              Phasellus consectetur sapien non lacus imperdiet dapibus. In\n              facilisis sed mi rutrum consequat. Sed augue sem diam.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n              <img src=\"../_images/shop/shop3.jpg\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n              <b>Better Control</b></h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Praesent\n              vitae erat. Integer aliquam, lorem vitae dapibus sollicitudin,\n              nibh nisl egestas enim, ut dapibus odio augue venenatis mi. Ut\n              tempus dui at mi semper, vel dapibus nisl consectetur. Phasellus\n              consectetur sapien non lacus imperdiet dapibus. In facilisis sed\n              mi rutrum consequat. Sed augue sem diam.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}}\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"img-wrapper mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n              <img src=\"../_images/shop/shop3.jpg\">\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .img-wrapper\">\n              <b>Workflow</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">\n              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer\n              aliquam, lorem vitae dapibus sollicitudin, nibh nisl egestas enim,\n              ut dapibus odio augue venenatis mi. Phasellus consectetur sapien\n              non lacus imperdiet dapibus.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
